CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 26, 1955, pg. A1 reads: "Handsome Pair - Mr. and Mrs. Edward T. Prather following their marriage Nov. 12. The bride is the former Miss Constance Louise Boyd. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of smiling Constance Louise Prather (Boyd) wearing headpiece with mid length veil, gown with floral lace overlay and crinoline skirt, holding book with ribbons and flowers in right hand, standing on stairs in interior, possibly on Dinwiddie Street, Hill District
